From 1954ec8dea80059f5e7c40813f3686c2fb08a25e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vivek Chettri <vchettri@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Thu, 3 Jul 2025 00:12:06 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] QSDK: DP Add fast path DP support for QoS features

For fast path QoS feature support, NSS queries the WLAN driver for  QoS
meta data
Based on the meta data, NSS updates the QoS Meta data in per packet
path.
Use the QoS meta provided by NSS to update the MSDUQ and QoS ID in per
packet path.

For Uplink SDWF, NSS calls the WLAN driver to apply uplink QoS

Add support for sending WMI for sending UL triggers when matching uplink
SDWF flow are indetified by NSS.

Signed-off-by: Vivek Chettri <vchettri@qti.qualcomm.com>
